title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 29 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 29 2022
description:
Waukesha murderer found guilty on all counts. Hochul says she doesn't regret covid mandates, tells New York parents to put their kids in masks again over new respiratory virus. Clay breaks down the latest polling and betting market data. Dems deploy their secret weapon: Kamala. Senator Ted Cruz joins Clay and Buck to discuss his new book: “Justice Corrupted: How the Left Weaponized Our Legal System,” as well as his experience battling libs in NYC this week, his outlook on the midterms and his Truth & Courage PAC bus tour. Another lie: Jim Crow 2.0. Flashback to caller who gave us advice on saving yourself from a python.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
